Description: [Onoda Sakamichi], a first-year student of Sohoku Highschool in Chiba, is a bit weak and loves anime. He was going to join the anime research club when he joined high school, but after his encounter with [Imaizumi Shunsuke], a boy well-renowned in the middle school cycling world, and [Naruko Shoukichi], a boy who won all the awards in Kansai`s cycling competition, he makes the decision to join the competitive cycling club. Hard training and other incidents wait for him in the Competitive Cycling Club, but unique seniors like [Kinjou], [Tadokoro], [Makishima], and many others support him as overcomes the many trials. Amidst those days of hard work, Sakamichi`s sleeping talent as a road racer begins to awaken!
